---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于龙虾助理 - 龙虾助理">
  <h1>🦞 关于龙虾助理</h1>
  <p class="lead">OpenClaw AI 助理的中文教程与知识分享平台</p>

  <div class="intro-section">
    <div class="intro-card">
      <h2>🎯 网站定位</h2>
      <p>龙虾助理是一个专注于 <strong>OpenClaw AI 助理</strong> 使用教程与知识分享的平台，致力于帮助用户从 0 开始"养"好属于自己的 AI 龙虾。</p>
      <p>在这里，你可以学习到如何让 AI 助理帮你处理文件、访问网络、执行代码、管理记忆，甚至自动化日常任务。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="intro-card highlight">
      <h2>🦞 为什么叫"龙虾"？</h2>
      <p>"龙虾"是 OpenClaw 的昵称，因为：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🦞 <strong>坚硬的外壳</strong> - 安全隔离，保护你的隐私</li>
        <li>🦞 <strong>灵活的双螯</strong> - 工具集成能力强，什么都能处理</li>
        <li>🦞 <strong>杂食性动物</strong> - 文件、网络、代码、记忆，样样精通</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features-section">
    <h2>✨ 网站特色</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
        <h3>体系化教程</h3>
        <p>从入门到进阶，从安全到实战，完整的学习路径让你循序渐进掌握 OpenClaw。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💡</div>
        <h3>实战案例</h3>
        <p>真实的自动化场景，包括查金价、写日报、监控价格、整理文件等，学完就能用。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>安全第一</h3>
        <p>详细的安全防护指南，教你正确配置权限、管理 API Key、防止 AI 误操作。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📰</div>
        <h3>最新资讯</h3>
        <p>追踪 OpenClaw 和 AI 助理领域的最新动态，不错过任何重要更新。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">❓</div>
        <h3>常见问题</h3>
        <p>持续更新的 FAQ 知识库，遇到问题先查这里，快速找到解决方案。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
        <h3>轻松幽默</h3>
        <p>"养龙虾"的比喻贯穿始终，让技术学习变得轻松有趣，不再枯燥。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section">
    <h2>📖 内容模块</h2>
    <div class="modules-list">
      <div class="module-item">
        <h3>🐣 入门教程</h3>
        <p>OpenClaw 是什么？如何安装部署？第一次配置怎么做？从这里开始你的 AI 助理之旅。</p>
        <div class="module-tags">
          <span class="tag">OpenClaw 介绍</span>
          <span class="tag">快速安装</span>
          <span class="tag">第一次对话</span>
          <span class="tag">工作区结构</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="module-item">
        <h3>📖 进阶使用</h3>
        <p>技能配置、工具集成、记忆系统、自动化任务...让你的 AI 龙虾越来越能干。</p>
        <div class="module-tags">
          <span class="tag">记忆系统</span>
          <span class="tag">技能配置</span>
          <span class="tag">浏览器自动化</span>
          <span class="tag">定时任务</span>
          <span class="tag">子代理</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="module-item">
        <h3>🛡️ 安全防护</h3>
        <p>API Key 管理、权限配置、数据隐私...确保你的 AI 助理安全可靠。</p>
        <div class="module-tags">
          <span class="tag">API Key 管理</span>
          <span class="tag">权限配置</span>
          <span class="tag">防止误操作</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="module-item">
        <h3>💼 实战案例</h3>
        <p>办公自动化、代码辅助、内容创作...看看别人怎么用 AI 龙虾提效。</p>
        <div class="module-tags">
          <span class="tag">查金价/股票</span>
          <span class="tag">写日报/周报</span>
          <span class="tag">价格监控</span>
          <span class="tag">整理文件</span>
          <span class="tag">旅行规划</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tech-section">
    <h2>🔧 技术栈</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-item">
        <h3>前端框架</h3>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">Astro 4.16</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">HTML5</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">CSS3</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-item">
        <h3>部署平台</h3>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">Vercel</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">CDN</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">HTTPS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-item">
        <h3>核心工具</h3>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">OpenClaw</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tech-item">
        <h3>设计规范</h3>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">响应式</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Noto Sans SC</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">龙虾红 #dc2626</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="team-section">
    <h2>👥 关于我们</h2>
    <div class="team-content">
      <p>龙虾助理是由 <strong>OpenClaw 中文社区</strong> 维护的公益项目，旨在帮助中文用户更好地使用 OpenClaw AI 助理。</p>
      <p>我们相信，AI 不应该是遥不可及的黑科技，而应该是每个人都能使用的日常工具。通过"养龙虾"的轻松比喻，我们让技术学习变得有趣，让更多人享受到 AI 带来的便利。</p>
      
      <div class="team-stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">22+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">教程文章</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">5</div>
          <div class="stat-label">内容模块</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">95%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">内容完成度</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">免费开放</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-section">
    <h2>🚀 开始学习</h2>
    <p>准备好开始你的 AI 助理之旅了吗？从入门教程开始，一步步成为养虾达人！</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/guide/" class="btn btn-primary">开始学习 →</a>
      <a href="/faq/" class="btn btn-secondary">查看 FAQ</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; }
    .intro-section { display: grid; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
    .intro-card { background: #f9fafb; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; }
    .intro-card.highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #ffffff 100%); }
    .intro-card h2 { margin-top: 0; }
    .intro-card ul { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    .intro-card li { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
    .features-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
    .features-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .feature-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; transition: all 0.3s; }
    .feature-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #dc2626; }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
    .feature-card p { color: #6b7280; margin: 0; }
    .content-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
    .content-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .modules-list { display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .module-item { background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .module-item h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #dc2626; }
    .module-item p { color: #6b7280; }
    .module-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .tag { background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .tech-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; background: #1f2937; color: white; padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; }
    .tech-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .tech-item h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #fca5a5; }
    .tech-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .tech-tag { background: #374151; color: #f3f4f6; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
    .team-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
    .team-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .team-content { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center; }
    .team-content p { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; color: #6b7280; }
    .team-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .stat-item { text-align: center; }
    .stat-number { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #dc2626; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .stat-label { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875rem; }
    .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 4rem 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #fecaca; }
    .cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-primary { background: #dc2626; color: white; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #b91c1c; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-secondary { background: white; color: #dc2626; border: 2px solid #dc2626; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: #fef2f2; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
